@host = http://localhost:5080

### Список устройств
GET {{host}}/api/devices

### Свет ВКЛ — разная яркость на каждый канал (0–255)
POST {{host}}/api/light
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceIndex": 1,
  "lightControllerSource": "On",
  "channels": [1, 2, 3, 4],
  "brightness": [50, 100, 150, 255]
}

### Свет ВЫКЛ
POST {{host}}/api/light
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceIndex": 1,
  "lightControllerSource": "Off",
  "channels": [1, 2, 3, 4]
}

### Вкл без brightness — на всех каналах 255
POST {{host}}/api/light
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceIndex": 1,
  "lightControllerSource": "On",
  "channels": [1, 2]
}
